17
00:01:30,041 --> 00:01:31,333
És louco?

18
00:01:31,416 --> 00:01:33,541
Estudante, trabalhador,

19
00:01:33,625 --> 00:01:35,750
pai, filha e herói.

20
00:01:36,458 --> 00:01:38,041
Boa sorte!

21
